				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Ah the elusive TinyDaggers. Only Place I know for certain is the Enchanters guild in Felwith(HighElf). They only cost a silver per so I suggest buying as MUCH as you can and bank the rest. Always keep a well stocked supply becuase I believe there is only 2 places to get them, HighElves and HighHumans(Erudians).
				</font>
