				The gypsy camp in the Oasis also has tiny silver ones. They go for a little over 1 silver. The camp is west from the the first water pillar near the dock. It can be seen during daytime as soon as you get on shore if your medding or hiding on the pillar. Watch out for sand giants while buying and if somebody shouts &quot;SG to p1&quot; run. That means &quot;sand giant coming to pillar 1&quot;.<BR>
Goodluck
